---
import WikiLayout from '../../layouts/WikiLayout.astro';
---

<WikiLayout title="Characters" section="characters" description="Meet the characters of Davy Jones' Deckhand — Thomas Essex, Davy Jones, Mary Read, and the full cast of this pirate roguelike deckbuilder. Backstories, lore, and key relationships.">
  <div class="wiki-content">
    <h1>Characters</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Davy Jones' Deckhand is driven by a cast of richly detailed characters — the reluctant hero,
      the cursed immortal, the pirate queen who never stopped running, and the girl who saw Tom
      when no one else did.
    </p>

    <div class="character-grid">
      <a href="/characters/thomas-essex" class="character-card">
        <img src="/images/characters/thomas-essex-thumb.png" alt="Thomas Essex" class="char-img" />
        <div class="char-info">
          <h3>Thomas Essex</h3>
          <p>A 17-year-old Portsmouth deckhand murdered by pirates, resurrected as Davy Jones' agent. Relentlessly optimistic, desperately hungry to be seen.</p>
          <span class="char-role">Protagonist</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/characters/davy-jones" class="character-card">
        <img src="/images/characters/davy-jones.png" alt="Davy Jones" class="char-img" />
        <div class="char-info">
          <h3>Davy Jones</h3>
          <p>A centuries-old immortal captain bound to the ocean depths, burning with stolen whale-oil fire. Ancient, terrible, and still desperately in love.</p>
          <span class="char-role">Antagonist / Employer</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/characters/mary-read" class="character-card">
        <img src="/images/characters/mary-read.png" alt="Mary Read" class="char-img" />
        <div class="char-info">
          <h3>Mary Read</h3>
          <p>Born Grace O'Malley, the Irish Pirate Queen. Around 190 years old, perpetually young, and still running from what she did to Davy Jones.</p>
          <span class="char-role">Antagonist</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</WikiLayout>

<style>
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .character-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .character-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--off-white);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .character-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(240,168,0,0.15);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .char-img {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    border-radius: 6px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .char-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .char-info p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .char-role {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .character-card:last-child:nth-child(odd) {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .character-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
